There's a fan letter for you.

17
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,000
More hate mail.

18
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,120
Haven't opened it.

19
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,200
Probably not.

20
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,520
Take a look.

21
